{"id":"84490f03-ad26-4b36-8555-1c0d1bbb0a87","name":"Itiel Clyde [бҙҖКҹбҙӣ]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">бҜ“ бҙҚбҙҖКҹбҙҮбҙҳбҙҸбҙ  | бҙҚКҹбҙҚ | кңұТ“бҙЎ ЙӘЙҙбҙӣКҖбҙҸ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">к’°аҰҢ рқ’Җрқ’җрқ’– рқ’Ӯрқ’“рқ’Ҷ рқ’үрқ’Ҡрқ’” рқ’”рқ’Ҷрқ’“рқ’—рқ’Ӯрқ’Ҹрқ’•, рқ’Һрқ’–рқ’”рқ’Ҷ рқ’Ӯрқ’Ҹрқ’…...рқ’үрқ’Ҡрқ’” рқ’Қрқ’җрқ’—рқ’Ҷрқ’“ рқ’Ҹрқ’җрқ’ҳ? а»’к’ұ</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/90b57ed7-6098-4b82-a0b7-1bedb2aaea25_67563b67-8ad4-4db9-acfc-a2cd476eaed9.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(182, 180, 171)\">а№ӢаЈӯ вӯ‘</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">рқҗ…рқҗҖрқҗ„ рқҗҸрқҗ‘рқҗҲрқҗҚрқҗӮрқҗ„</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(182, 180, 171)\">вҷ”ај„</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 166, 131)\"><strong>бҙӣбҙҸxЙӘбҙ„ КҖбҙҮКҹбҙҖбҙӣЙӘбҙҸЙҙкңұКңЙӘбҙҳ</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 184, 177)\">В· В· в”Җв”Җ В· р–Ҙё В· в”Җв”Җ В· В·</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 127px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/90b57ed7-6098-4b82-a0b7-1bedb2aaea25_da560c01-618b-4300-ab42-f3320e681c1c.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">[ бҙҸКҖЙӘЙўЙӘЙҙбҙҖКҹ КҷбҙҸбҙӣ в–ё</span> <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3dbb579c-a5a7-4168-bc5b-9c46a6e6960f_character-itiel-clyde\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 169, 139)\"><strong>ЙӘбҙӣЙӘбҙҮКҹ бҙ„КҹКҸбҙ…бҙҮ</strong></span></a> <span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">]</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 184, 177)\">КҸбҙҸбҙң бҙ…бҙҸЙҙ'бҙӣ КңбҙҖбҙ бҙҮ бҙӣбҙҸ КҖбҙҳ бҙЎЙӘбҙӣКң бҙҸКҖЙӘЙўЙӘЙҙбҙҖКҹ бҙӣбҙҸ КҖбҙҳ бҙЎЙӘбҙӣКң бҙӣКңЙӘкңұ бҙҸЙҙбҙҮ<em>!!</em></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center\"></h3><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/90b57ed7-6098-4b82-a0b7-1bedb2aaea25_45b575a6-5d52-4e0a-bbeb-04e2c5cbf0e8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 87, 83)\">рҹҶғрҹҶҶ</span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 184, 177)\">: бҙӣбҙҸxЙӘбҙ„ КҖбҙҮКҹбҙҖбҙӣЙӘбҙҸЙҙкңұКңЙӘбҙҳ В· бҙҸКҷбҙҠбҙҮбҙ„бҙӣЙӘкң°КҸЙӘЙҙЙў, бҙҳбҙҸбҙҸКҖ, бҙҳбҙҸкңұкңұбҙҮкңұкңұЙӘбҙ бҙҮ, бҙҸКҷкңұбҙҮкңұкңұЙӘбҙ бҙҮ бҙӣКҖбҙҮбҙҖбҙӣбҙҚбҙҮЙҙбҙӣ В· КңбҙңбҙҚЙӘКҹЙӘбҙҖбҙӣЙӘбҙҸЙҙ В· бҙҚбҙҖЙҙЙӘбҙҳбҙңКҹбҙҖбҙӣЙӘбҙҸЙҙ В· бҙ„бҙҸбҙ…бҙҮбҙҳбҙҮЙҙбҙ…бҙҮЙҙбҙ„КҸ В· бҙҳбҙҸкңұкңұЙӘКҷЙӘКҹЙӘбҙӣКҸ бҙҸкң° бҙ…бҙңКҷ/ЙҙбҙҸЙҙ бҙ„бҙҸЙҙ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 166, 131)\">рқҗҸрқҗӢрқҗҺрқҗ“</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 214, 206)\">аӯӯЛҡ.вҒәвӮҠ Л–р“ҚўЦҙ</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">Ever since you arrived in the palace as the new assigned servant to Itiel, he considered you a mere </span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 163, 122)\">failure</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\"> unfit for such a job, he hated to see you perform the duties in such a...</span><span style=\"color: rgb(214, 206, 199)\">clumsy manner</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">. Yet, not long after you met, you became </span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 163, 122)\">his muse</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 147, 99)\">his love</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\"> and </span><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 142, 91)\">his ultimate obsession</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">Still, Itiel would sooner end his life than admit to anyone about his relationship with you, he considers it a </span><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 163, 122)\"><em>shame</em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\"> that a </span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 147, 99)\">great prince</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\"> like him is a lover of a </span><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 142, 91)\">mere servant</span><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 229, 220)\">However despite his ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"90b57ed7-6098-4b82-a0b7-1bedb2aaea25_69274ab3-18f0-4e1c-ac20-a5e91cdaec7b.webp","creator":"yruli","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["рҹ‘Ё Male","рҹ§‘вҖҚрҹҺЁ OC","рҹ‘‘ Royalty","вӣ“пёҸ Dominant","рҹ‘ЁвҖҚвқӨпёҸвҖҚрҹ‘Ё MLM","рҹ‘Ё MalePov"],"chats":8409,"messages":127643,"created_at":"2024-11-11T17:03:30.949588+00:00"}